name: Downpours Of Disapproval CD
description:
DOWNPOURS OF DISAPPROVAL
Brand new full cd; out 06.09.2013!

-> Recorded, mixed and produced by Jochem Jacobs at Split Second Sound Studio, Amsterdam, Holland (Textures, The Red Shore, Severe Torture…)
-> Mastered by Alan Douches @ West West Side Music, NY, USA (Whitechapel, The Black Dahlia Murder, Job For A Cowboy, Madball…)
-> Artwork by Dennis Sibeijen for Damnengine (All Shall Perish, Chimaira, Molotov Solution…)
-> Guest appearances by Daniel (Textures), Brent (Steak Number Eight), Navene Koperweis (ex-Animals As Leaders) & DJ Jeant
-> 51 minutes, 11 tracks. 
-> The extensive 16 page booklet contains writer notes commenting every song, giving a deeper insight into the lyrical content.

Tracklist: 
1. Resurrection
2. Downpours Of Disapproval
3. How Much Does Life Weigh?
4. Stillborn
5. Testify
6. Trapped
7. Vengeance Is Mine
8. Culture Of Cancellations
9. The Generation Chasm
10. Le Coup De Grâce
* Show Me Your Hands That Strangled My Child (bonus track)

Stickers, posters…free with every order! 
(As long as we’ve got some left.)

name: Fragments Of Awareness CD
description: Our second full cd! Recorded, mixed and mastered at CCR studio (Aborted, In-Quest, Morda, Blood Redemption…). The bass-recordings were done at Svenchi Janssens’ (Aborted bas-player) home studio. Guestvocals on this album by our friends Bart (Rafflesia), Didah & Dominick (It Breeds No More) & Gaetan (When Blood Burns). Artwork by Avernus Studios (The Black Dahlia Murder, White Chapel, Aborted…). 44 minutes, 11 tracks, more brutal ànd melodic than ever before! The extensive booklet contains liner notes commenting every song, giving a deeper insight into the lyrical content. Tracklist: 1. Forsaken 2. If I’d Become A Father 3. Omen Of Catastrophe 4. With All Due Respect 5. Sworn Persistence 6. The Suicide Circle 7. Cauterize Havoc 8. Cordoba 9. Solace 10. A Period Of Consequences 11. Regenesis Check out: Sworn Persistence, Forsaken & If I’d Become A Father @ the Crimson Falls MySpace page Stickers, posters…free with every order! (As long as we’ve got some left.)

name: The Dead E.P.
description:
This is a concept E.P. build around the theme of the first World War & the songs ‘In Flanders Fields’ & ‘We Are The Dead’ which were already featured on our debut full cd ‘The True Face Of Human Nature. 

This release includes a Dutch version of the song ‘In Flanders Fields’ (‘In Vlaanderens Velden’) and the first recording of the song ‘Cordoba’, which we rerecorded for our second full cd ‘Fragments Of Awareness’. A special release for the die-hard Crimson Falls fan!

Tracklist:
1.      In Flanders Fields
2.      We Are The Dead
3.      In Vlaanderens Velden
4.      Cordoba

Released on 01.12.2008 by Regenesis Records
  
Stickers, posters, postcards…free with every order! 
(As long as we’ve got some left.)

name: The True Face Of Human Nature CD
description: Our first full length release! Recorded, mixed and mastered at CCR studio (Aborted, In-Quest, Betzefer, Liar, Lengtche…). ‘The True Face Of Human Nature’ brings you 45 minutes of modern & hard-hitting deathMETALcore. The album features guest appearances by Svencho (Aborted) on ‘Controle Alt Delete’ and XCaroX (No Recess) on ‘Martyr Vs. Terrorist’. The artwork is conceived by Avernus Studios, a new design agency born out of the ashes of Dirge Design (Immolation, The Amenta, In-Quest…). The extensive booklet contains liner notes commenting every song, giving a deeper insight on the lyrical content. Tracklist: 1. Abort Every Weakness 2. Erase All Fear 3. Architecture Disavowed 4. Controle Alt Delete 5. Prelude To The Cataclysm 6. Four Slaves, Four Struggles 7. Martyr Vs. Terrorist 8. Poetry For The Scum 9. In Flanders Fields 10. We Are The Dead 11. Book Of Memories 12. The True Face Of Human Nature Listen too: Controle Alt Delete & The True Face Of Human Nature @ the Crimson Falls MySpace page Stickers, posters…free with every order! (As long as we’ve got some left.)

name: Ruins 2K5 MCD
description: Our debut mcd containing five uncompromising pieces of modern & energetic death metal/metalcore. This album was recorded and mix at AK Studios (Liar, Lengtche). Mastering done at Zigzound (DK) (Ill-Disposed, Aborted, Hatesphere). Tracklist: 1. When The Blood Becomes Adrenaline 2. Water Mirrors Sorrow 3. The Crimson Eyed 4. Book Of Memories 5. Behold The Crimson Falls Artwork by Dirge Design (Immolation, The Amenta, In-Quest…). Check out: Water Mirrors Sorrow @ the Crimson Falls MySpace page Stickers, posters, postcards…free with every order! (As long as we’ve got some left.)
